Interface FirmwareUpdateHandler

All Superinterfaces:
FirmwareUpdateHandlerBase, PrinterReconnectionHandler
public interface FirmwareUpdateHandler extends FirmwareUpdateHandlerBase, PrinterReconnectionHandler
Handler class is used to update status while performing a firmware download and to notify the caller when the printer has reconnected after restarting.
